    {
      "beat_id": "B02",
      "t_start": 9.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "De Broglie said: a particle with momentum p has wavelength h over p. The same formula that describes an electron also describes a person \u2014 the only question is what number comes out.",
