      "t_start": 28.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9.0,
      "narration_text": "Plug in the numbers. A seventy kilogram person walking at one meter per second has momentum seventy kilogram-meters-per-second. De Broglie wavelength: six point six times ten to the minus thirty-four, divided by seventy \u2014 that is ten to the minus thirty-five meters.",
